description:
I had to say "cabbage" at the end because I'd miscounted the number of e's used in the video. There were only 123. But if I re-recorded and said "one hundred twenty three" there'd then be 125 e's. But if I said "one hundred twenty five," there'd be 124. But if i said "one hundred twenty four" it'd be back to 123. So I decided to just add "cabbage" at the end 💅

#nationalholiday #calendar #history #past #future #counting #cabbage
title: History Is Accumulating
